sights.name: Turku Castle
sights.quote: 13th-century castle housing museum tracing its history from medieval fort to renaissance palace.

sights.name: Luostarinmäki
sights.quote: Handicrafts museum housed in craftsmen's wooden dwellings that survived the city's major 1827 fire.

sights.name: Turku Art Museum
sights.quote: Imposing, 20th-century museum housing notable Nordic, surrealist & pop art collections.

sights.name: Aboa Vetus & Ars Nova
sights.quote: Contemporary art & history museum housed in a former palace with underground archaeological ruins.

sights.name: Turku Cathedral
sights.quote: Iconic Lutheran church, restored after an 1827 fire, with frescoes, royal tombs & religious museum.

sights.name: Forum Marinum
sights.quote: Historic tall ships & Finnish naval vessels on display in maritime & naval museums in a shipyard.

sights.name: Pharmacy Museum and Qwensel house
sights.quote: 1700s wooden house with displays about the pharmacy that operated here in the 1800s.

sights.name: Wäinö Aaltonen Museum of Art
sights.quote: International modern art museum with a major collection of the eponymous Finnish sculptor's work.

sights.name: Michael´s Church
sights.quote: Neo-Gothic redbrick church consecrated in 1905 with a 252-foot steeple & 3 vaulted interior isles.

sights.name: The Old Great Square
sights.quote: Eminent square with grand buildings & a historic trade & administration hub up to the 19th century.

sights.name: Sibeliusmuseum
sights.quote: Museum with a collection of instruments, sheet music & recordings, plus a seasonal concert series.

sights.name: Turku Biological Museum
sights.quote: Nature museum in an art nouveau building since 1907 with dioramas depicting Finland's flora & fauna.

sights.name: Moomin World
sights.quote: Moomin World theme park, with costumed characters, regular live shows & activities, open in summer.

sights.name: Kurjenrahka National Park
sights.quote: Established in 1998, this national park includes primeval forests, hiking trails & camping shelters.

sights.name: Shopping center Skanssi
sights.quote: Airy shopping center featuring national & global brands as well as cafes & casual restaurants.

sights.name: Zoolandia
sights.quote: Inside/outside kids' activity center with adventure playground, paddling pool & animal enclosures.

sights.name: Escape Artist Room Escape - pakohuone Turku
